# Financial Risk Credit Credit Exposures Newly Impaired Amount

## identifier
de7744

## type
float

## definition
This is the value of all exposures of the reporting party that give rise to counterparty credit risk, determined in accordance with the relevant prudential standards, that have been newly classified as impaired during the relevant period.

## syntax
### xbrl
- balance=debit
- name=FinancialRisk.Credit.CreditExposuresNewlyImpaired.Amount
- classification=baf/bafot/bafot.02.06
- period=duration
